      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.Item.w0qoJvrAY75dNJkt]{Esotericist}</p>\n<p>When you regain your spell slots for the day, you gain one additional spell slot of the highest level of spell you can cast. You cannot use this spell slot to cast a spell that affects hybrid or technological items, nor can you use the spell slot to cast a spell that affects creatures that have the technological subtype. If you attempt to do any of these, the spell fails and the spell slot is used up for the day.</p>"
